Usage Example:
// Start with simple coffee
Coffee myCoffee =
new SimpleCoffee();
// Cost: $2.00
// Add milk decorator
myCoffee =
new WithMilk(myCoffee);
// Cost: $2.50
// Add sugar decorator
myCoffee =
new WithSugar(myCoffee);
// Cost: $2.70
System.out.println(
myCoffee.getDescription());
// "Simple coffee, with milk,
// with sugar"
